    <detaileddescription>
<para><xrefsect id="deprecated_1_deprecated000035"><xreftitle>Deprecated</xreftitle><xrefdescription><para>use <ref refid="structopenthread__state__changed__callback" kindref="compound">openthread_state_changed_callback</ref> instead.</para>
</xrefdescription></xrefsect></para>
<para>OpenThread state change callback structure</para>
<para>Used to register a callback in the callback list. As many callbacks as needed can be added as long as each of them are unique pointers of struct <ref refid="structopenthread__state__changed__cb" kindref="compound">openthread_state_changed_cb</ref>. Beware such structure should not be allocated on stack. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
